          "author_association": "NONE",
          "active_lock_reason": null,
          "body": "When having this configuration:\n\n``` javascript\nvar webpackConfig = {\n    entry: {\n        sdk: ['./src/sdk.js']\n    },\n    output: {\n        filename: './dist/sdk.js'\n    },\n    bail: false\n};\n```\n\nany errors (syntax, mostly) are not cleared in watch mode upon rebuilds.\n\nBelow the details.\n### Case 1 - working as expected\n\n**Confguration**\n\n``` javascript\nvar webpackConfig = {\n    entry: './src/sdk.js',\n    output: {\n        filename: './dist/sdk.js'\n    }\n    bail: false\n};\n```\n\n**`sdk.js` file**\n\n``` javascript\nvar a = 10;\n```\n\n**Initial result**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830138/4fb7310c-592b-11e5-8e51-5a81192671f8.png)\n\n**intentionally incorrect `sdk.js` file**\n\n``` javascript\nvar a =;\n```\n\n**Result for incorrect `sdk.js` file**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830173/ccc8bf02-592c-11e5-8a8d-71c258b40f58.png)\n\nNow, restoring the `sdk.js` file back to **correct state** produces:\n\n**Result for fixed `sdk.js` file**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830183/2111fcae-592d-11e5-967e-0155e1841537.png)\n### Case 2 - not working as expected\n\nSame `sdk.js` file, _slightly_ different configuration.\n\n**Confguration**\n\n``` javascript\nvar webpackConfig = {\n    entry: {\n        sdk: ['./src/sdk.js']\n    },\n    output: {\n        filename: './dist/sdk.js'\n    },\n    bail: false\n};\n```\n\n**`sdk.js` file**\n\n``` javascript\nvar a = 10;\n```\n\n**Initial result**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830198/a35ab05c-592d-11e5-8f57-f247cc2db67d.png)\n\n**intentionally incorrect `sdk.js` file**\n\n``` javascript\nvar a =;\n```\n\n**Result for incorrect `sdk.js` file**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830206/db404a22-592d-11e5-8b9f-cad9d0670aa6.png)\n\nNow, restoring the `sdk.js` file back to **correct state** produces:\n\n**Result for fixed `sdk.js` file**\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830214/07aadd7a-592e-11e5-8794-8228c1c1ecf5.png)\n\n---\n\nMoreover, doing the same break-fix sequence multiple time results in:\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1825272/9830218/3371e700-592e-11e5-8b50-8d98ef0594d6.png)\n"
