          "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nPreviously storybook just tried to glob the provided globPattern.\r\nIt new joins the glob pattern with the configDir resulting in the glob not matching anything.\r\n\r\nIn my case I'm using another globbing library and all paths are already resolved.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nGlobs before [this change](https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/pull/10926/files#r439078951) should still work.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\n\r\nYou can see that storybook is joining my configDir with the provided glob (in the case a full path)\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-06-11 at 2 28 01 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1192452/84440972-c3478880-abef-11ea-9ef0-ef325e864e1b.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Code snippets**\r\nIf applicable, add code samples to help explain your problem.\r\n\r\n**System:**\r\n\r\nbeta-25\r\n\r\n"
