          "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nno-args warning is not being shown if argTypes are being used. For me this became a problem when I tried to define two stories in the same file: one using `args` and `argTypes`, and the other without args.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Create a simple tsx story, with no args configured\r\n2. Run `yarn storybook` and see the warning\r\n3. Add an `argType`\r\n4. See that warning is not being shown anymore.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nStories not configured to handle controls should show warning even if `argTypes` is being used.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nWithout `argTypes`\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17753656/84043718-08b04f80-a97d-11ea-8f97-97600cf94218.png)\r\n\r\nWith `argTypes`\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17753656/84043859-31d0e000-a97d-11ea-8d1b-ad5a0036c44c.png)\r\n\r\n**Code snippets**\r\nWithout `argTypes`: \r\n```\r\nimport React, { FC } from 'react'\r\nimport { Button } from './Button'\r\n\r\nexport default {\r\n    title: 'Button',\r\n    component: Button\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport const Basic = (): FC => {\r\n    return <Button />\r\n}\r\n```\r\nWith `argTypes`: \r\n```\r\nimport React, { FC } from 'react'\r\nimport { Button } from './Button'\r\n\r\nexport default {\r\n    title: 'Button',\r\n    component: Button,\r\n    argTypes: {\r\n        background: { control: { type: 'color' } }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport const Basic = (): FC => {\r\n    return <Button />\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n**System:**\r\n\r\n  System:\r\n    OS: Linux 5.3 Ubuntu 18.04.3 LTS (Bionic Beaver)\r\n    CPU: (4) x64 Intel(R) Core(TM) i5-6500 CPU @ 3.20GHz\r\n  Binaries:\r\n    Node: 12.1.0 - ~/.nvm/versions/node/v12.1.0/bin/node\r\n    Yarn: 1.17.3 - ~/.yarn/bin/yarn\r\n    npm: 5.1.0 - ~/dev/intelie/liverig/live-plugins/node_modules/.bin/npm\r\n  Browsers:\r\n    Chrome: 78.0.3904.97\r\n    Firefox: 76.0.1\r\n  npmPackages:\r\n    @storybook/addon-controls: ^6.0.0-beta.22 => 6.0.0-beta.22 \r\n    @storybook/addon-docs: ^6.0.0-beta.22 => 6.0.0-beta.22 \r\n    @storybook/addon-links: ^6.0.0-beta.22 => 6.0.0-beta.22 \r\n    @storybook/addons: ^6.0.0-beta.22 => 6.0.0-beta.22 \r\n    @storybook/react: ^6.0.0-beta.22 => 6.0.0-beta.22 \r\n\r\n"
