          "author_association": "NONE",
          "active_lock_reason": null,
          "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nWhen passing the `docsOnly: true`  parameter to a .mdx story that is hoisting a CSF story there is a render loop within that story  display that appears to rerender the MDX story in place of the expected CSF story output.\r\n\r\nBehavior appears to have started with 6.0 Beta 15\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nUse the following stories to reproduce the behavior based on the official-storybook examples.\r\n\r\n**csf-with-mdx-docs.stories.js**\r\n```\r\nimport React from 'react'\r\n\r\nexport default {\r\n  title: 'Addons/Docs/csf-with-mdx-docs',\r\n  includeStories: [], // or don't load this file at all\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport const basic = () => <div>Test</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**csf-with-mdx-docs.stories.mdx**\r\n```\r\nimport { Meta, Story, Preview } from '@storybook/addon-docs/blocks';\r\nimport * as stories from './csf-with-mdx-docs.stories.js';\r\n\r\n<Meta title=\"Addons/Docs/csf-with-mdx-docs\" \r\nparameters={{\r\n    docsOnly: true,\r\n    }}\r\n/>\r\n\r\n# Button\r\n\r\nI can define a story with the function imported from CSF:\r\n\r\n<Preview>\r\n<Story name=\"basic\">{stories.basic}</Story>\r\n</Preview>\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nThe basic story exported via CSF should render within Preview block.  This is the behavior if the `docsOnly: true` parameter is removed.  With the parameter active the repeated re-rendering occurs.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nExample screenshot.\r\n\r\n![Screen Shot 2020-05-28 at 7 01 40 AM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61430182/83144955-483f8780-a0b1-11ea-8753-c9a7441ccbf4.png)\r\n\r\n**System:**\r\nEnvironment Info:\r\n\r\n  System:\r\n    OS: macOS Mojave 10.14.6\r\n    CPU: (12) x64 Intel(R) Core(TM) i9-8950HK CPU @ 2.90GHz\r\n  Binaries:\r\n    Node: 10.19.0 - /usr/local/bin/node\r\n    Yarn: 1.22.4 - /usr/local/bin/yarn\r\n    npm: 6.13.7 - /usr/local/bin/npm\r\n  Browsers:\r\n    Chrome: 83.0.4103.61\r\n    Firefox: 76.0.1\r\n    Safari: 13.1\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nThe docsOnly parameter was working as expected on prior 6.0 Betas before 15.\r\n"
