          "author_association": "MEMBER",
          "active_lock_reason": null,
          "body": "#10373 intended to reduce the data sent over the channel on app startup by \"normalizing\" story parameters (e.g. sending component-level parameters once per component rather than once per story).\r\n\r\nIt appears that component ArgTypes are being sent per-story rather than per-component, thus losing out on a performance opportunity. Need to fix the `argTypes` extractor to do the right thing."
