          "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nWhen storybook fails to load, the manager is showing button \"View error\" but clicking on that button leads to another error.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nCheck #10655 for a breaking storybook on load\r\n- start-storybook\r\n- view error\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nError displayed\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nIf applicable, add screenshots to help explain your problem.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/599163/81786887-8b6df800-9500-11ea-95a2-e4a44b3142bf.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/599163/81786854-7f823600-9500-11ea-949a-5ae57466548c.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/599163/81786977-a9d3f380-9500-11ea-9526-b7b67d5561b1.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"
