          "author_association": "NONE",
          "active_lock_reason": null,
          "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nPreview is not loaded when addon docs panel is renamed in `manager.js`, refreshing page after initial load fixes the preview. Issue may be caused by wrong iframe URL (https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/issues/10648)\r\n\r\n```js\r\nimport addons from \"@storybook/addons\";\r\n\r\naddons.setConfig({\r\n  previewTabs: {\r\n    \"storybook/docs/panel\": { title: \"Usage\" },\r\n    canvas: { title: \"Sandbox\" },\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1199\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-13 at 08 28 46\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/21260478/81778924-f9f88900-94f3-11ea-90ca-2bbb2bba4075.png\">\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nRename addon docs panel.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nPreview should load.\r\n\r\n**System:**\r\n```\r\nEnvironment Info:\r\n\r\n  System:\r\n    OS: macOS 10.15.4\r\n    CPU: (8) x64 Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-4770HQ CPU @ 2.20GHz\r\n  Binaries:\r\n    Node: 12.16.1 - ~/.nvm/versions/node/v12.16.1/bin/node\r\n    Yarn: 1.17.3 - /usr/local/bin/yarn\r\n    npm: 6.13.4 - ~/.nvm/versions/node/v12.16.1/bin/npm\r\n  Browsers:\r\n    Chrome: 81.0.4044.138\r\n    Firefox: 76.0.1\r\n    Safari: 13.1\r\n  npmPackages:\r\n    @storybook/addon-actions: 6.0.0-beta.6 => 6.0.0-beta.6 \r\n    @storybook/addon-docs: 6.0.0-beta.6 => 6.0.0-beta.6 \r\n    @storybook/addon-links: 6.0.0-beta.6 => 6.0.0-beta.6 \r\n    @storybook/addons: 6.0.0-beta.6 => 6.0.0-beta.6 \r\n    @storybook/react: 6.0.0-beta.6 => 6.0.0-beta.6 \r\n```\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n`preview.js`\r\n\r\n```js\r\nimport { addParameters } from \"@storybook/react\";\r\nimport { DocsPage, DocsContainer } from \"@storybook/addon-docs/blocks\";\r\n\r\naddParameters({\r\n  viewMode: 'docs',\r\n  docs: {\r\n    container: DocsContainer,\r\n    page: DocsPage,\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n"
